description:
Subscribe for more Pitch Meetings: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Kq-yEt1iYsbUzNOoIRK0g

Minecraft is popular! And therefore it must have a movie! One of the most successful games of all time has finally been adapted to the big screen, and it’s led to quite a few mini-riots involving a chicken jockey. Go figure.

A Minecraft Movie definitely raises some questions. Like who is the main character? Are those weird diamonds even worth anything? Why did the chicken jockey drive everyone insane?

To answer all of these questions and more, step inside Ryan George’s Pitch Meeting for A Minecraft Movie!
